---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="pt-16 pb-12 px-6 bg-[#FDFCFB] border-t border-black/5 text-deepblack">
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
    
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start md:flex-row md:justify-between gap-12 md:gap-16 mb-12">
      
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start space-y-6 max-w-sm">
        <h2 class="font-serif italic text-2xl tracking-tight">Kadô-Kou</h2>
        <p class="text-xs leading-[1.8] text-coolgrey tracking-widest text-center md:text-left uppercase">
          L'art de l'attention.<br/> 
          La gestion d'événements pour l'esthète contemporain.
        </p>
      </div>

      <nav class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-10 md:gap-x-24" aria-label="Liens du pied de page">
        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h3 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-coolgrey/60">
            Légal
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li><a href="/mentions-legales" class="text-xs md:text-[13px] hover:text-brushedgold transition-all duration-500 ease-out">Mentions</a></li>
            <li><a href="/cgu" class="text-xs md:text-[13px] hover:text-brushedgold transition-all duration-500 ease-out">CGU</a></li>
            <li><a href="/confidentialite" class="text-xs md:text-[13px] hover:text-brushedgold transition-all duration-500 ease-out">Confidentialité</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h3 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-coolgrey/60">
            Service
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li><a href="/centre-aide" class="text-xs md:text-[13px] hover:text-brushedgold transition-all duration-500 ease-out">Aide</a></li>
            <li><a href="mailto:contact@kadoko.fr" class="text-xs md:text-[13px] hover:text-brushedgold transition-all duration-500 ease-out italic">Contact</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-8 border-t border-black/3 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brushedgold/40"></span>
        <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-coolgrey">Toulouse • France</p>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-xs tracking-widest text-coolgrey">
        &copy; {currentYear} — Kadô-Kou. Tous droits réservés.
      </p>

      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="https://instagram.com/kadoko" class="opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" aria-label="Suivre sur Instagram">
          <span class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase" aria-hidden="true">Ig</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://x.com/kadoko" class="opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" aria-label="Suivre sur X (Twitter)">
          <span class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase" aria-hidden="true">X</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  footer {
    font-feature-settings: "kern" 1, "tnum" 1;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  a {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  a::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 0;
    height: 1px;
    bottom: -2px;
    left: 0;
    background-color: currentColor;
    transition: width 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1);
  }

  a:hover::after {
    width: 100%;
  }
</style>